      "body" : "No. The content of the QR code does not need to be a URI.  Granted, though, the QR codes being used have a URI with a \"bitcoin:\" prefix.\r\n\r\nIf there are any dedicated readers for just webcams that launch a URI handler, I haven't seen them for Windows/Mac/Linux.  Does Bitcoin Core have a URI handler for such \"bitcoin:\" URI's?",
